reviewText: needed to replace like DVD at church. This was it
Life saver as we lost the one that came in our VBS packet.  Fast shipping.  Thanks.
I love having a dvd with the music and actions.  Makes things easy!
quick delivery.  Just what I needed for children's program
fabulous collection of songs and videos which will work really well in our kids church.
I loved this DVD. The Children in our Childrens ministry absoutly enjoyed it. It brought a new envioriment to the class.

We used Power Lab as a VBS when it came out.  Group Publishing has great music and these music videos with lyrics on the bottom for kids to follow are great.  They are great for use at home for kids to play, sing, dance and worship too!  But they are also great to use at church.  We have been reusing our old VBS kits and using them in Children's Worship.
